'''东地中海地区'''指的是位于[[地中海|地中海]]东部（[[黎凡特海|黎凡特海]]）的[[西亚|西亚]] 地区，包括[[大敘利亞|叙利亚]]（[[黎凡特|黎凡特]]）地区、[[賽普勒斯|塞浦路斯]]、[[安納托利亞|安纳托利亚]]和[[埃及|埃及]]。更为广泛的定义可能还包括 [[东南欧|欧洲东南部]]的[[土耳其|土耳其]]的欧洲部分（东色雷斯）、[[希腊|希腊]]和[[阿尔巴尼亚|阿尔巴尼亚]]。该地区的各个民族拥有共同的美食传统、风俗习惯和悠久而相互交织的历史<ref>{{Cite web|title=Eastern Mediterranean Political Map|url=http://shop.nationalgeographic.com/ngs/product/maps/wall-maps/countries-and-region-maps/eastern-mediterranean-political-map|accessdate=17 October 2011|work=[[National_Geographic|National Geographic]] Store|publisher=[[National_Geographic_Society|National Geographic Society]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180221161558/https://shop.nationalgeographic.com/product/maps/wall-maps/countries-and-region-maps/eastern-mediterranean-political-map|archivedate=2018-02-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Ancient Ashkelon|url=http://ngm.nationalgeographic.com/features/world/asia/israel/ashkelon-text.html|last=Gore|first=Rick|date=17 October 2002|journal=|publisher=[[National_Geographic_Society|National Geographic Society]]|accessdate=17 October 2011|editor-last=Clark|editor-first=Robert|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120716031123/http://ngm.nationalgeographic.com/features/world/asia/israel/ashkelon-text.html|archivedate=2012-07-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-15479879|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|title=The state of Israel: Internal influence driving change|date=6 November 2011|accessdate=4 October 2018|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|first=Tim|author=Franks|authorlink=|archive-date=2020-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709042802/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-15479879|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Orfalea|first=Gregory|authorlink=|title=The Arab Americans: A History|publisher=Olive Branch Press|location=Northampton, MA|year=2006|page=[https://archive.org/details/arabamericans00greg/page/249 249]|url=https://archive.org/details/arabamericans00greg|isbn=9781566565974}}</ref> 。 

== 地区 ==
[[File:A-3-37-69-East-Meditteranean.jpg|左]]
东地中海地区通常有两种理解方式： 

* 更广义上的黎凡特，包括狭义上的黎凡特以及历史上与其紧密联系的相邻地区，即阿尔巴尼亚、希腊和埃及。 
* [[大敘利亞|叙利亚地区]]与[[賽普勒斯|塞浦路斯岛]]（也称为[[黎凡特|黎凡特]]）以及[[土耳其|土耳其]] ，该定义仅限于[[西亚|西亚]]。 

